title: Events
description: "EISS activities and events — multi-year research programmes, plus online and hybrid roundtables, seminars, and doctoral training workshops open to everyone in European security studies."
metaImage: /assets/images/events-meta.jpg
navKey: events
lang: en
alternates:
  en: /events.html
